{
  "id": "adv_event_2402_01_02",
  "title": "あなた達は\nもしかして",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-snow-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "着いたわね、北海道！\n一面が真っ白な雪景色……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’re here‚ Hokkaido!\nA pure white snowy landscape…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.787369823500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "これは確かに絶景だね\nたまにしか降らない都内の雪とは大違いだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s truly a magnificent view.\nIt’s very different from the snow that occasionally falls in Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0007031282,
      "endTime": 12.976100047500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 13.1827667714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "私も新鮮だわ……。岡山でも地元は降らない地域\nだったから。ほら、こころもこっちに――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s refreshing for me too…. In Okayama‚ my hometown was in an area where it didn’t snow.\nCome on‚ Kokoro‚ over here――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1827667714,
      "endTime": 20.7654880048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 20.8921542963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "さ……\n寒いですーーー！！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "C-C-\nColdーーー!!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8921542963,
      "endTime": 25.7556918939,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 25.9690251749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "こ……こんなに寒いだなんて……！\n聞いてないですよ～～！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-S-So… cold…!\nNo one told me it would be this cold!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.9690251749,
      "endTime": 32.0814288538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 32.2947621108
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "いや、空港で言ったでしょ……\n舐めてると地獄を見るよって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I told you at the airport…\nThat you’d see hell if you underestimated it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2947621108,
      "endTime": 37.8958051444,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 38.0824718397
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "余ってるカイロあげるから\n上着もしっかり着込んで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ take my extra hand warmers.\nand make sure you bundle up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0824718397,
      "endTime": 42.0133562487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 42.2266895534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……\n結局愛のお世話になるのね、こころは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly…\nKokoro‚ you’re always relying on Ai…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.2266895534,
      "endTime": 47.1581635715,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、いつものことじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it’s not like it’s unusual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.3581635715,
      "endTime": 49.8447394611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そういう二人も、空港出る前に\n大量のカイロを開けていたような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You two were also opening a ton of hand warmers\nbefore we left the airport…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0380727849,
      "endTime": 55.8825623593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "……見間違いじゃないかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You must’ve been mistaken.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.0758963031,
      "endTime": 57.581724016100004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 57.7883906446
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう。気のせいだから忘れていいと思うよ\nそんなことより……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ right. It was just your imagination‚ so you can forget about it.\nMore importantly…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7883906446,
      "endTime": 63.3565991483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 63.556599339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "この後はどうするの？\n僕、ちょっとお腹空いてきちゃったんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are we doing after this?\nI’m getting a little hungry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.556599339,
      "endTime": 68.7246718487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "昼食にはいい時間かもしれないな\nチェックインまでまだ時間もあるし、先に食事を――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This might be a good time for lunch.\nWe still have time before check-in‚ so let’s have lunch――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9246720395,
      "endTime": 74.7079600415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 74.8812907936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ホテル！　ホテル、行きましょう！！\nロビー、暖かい！　ここ、寒い！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hotel! Hotel‚ let’s go!!\nThe lobby is warm! It’s cold here!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.8812907936,
      "endTime": 81.21471469410001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 81.4280481419
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "寒さで片言になってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cold is making her speak in short sentences…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4280481419,
      "endTime": 84.28178959700001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 84.4684561969
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくなら、さっきのリストのお店に行きたいな\n味噌ラーメンとかスープカレーとか、温まれる所",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If we’re going to eat‚ I want to go to one of the places on the list from earlier.\nSomewhere we can warm up‚ like a miso ramen or soup curry place.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4684561969,
      "endTime": 92.0578214885,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 92.2578212978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ごはん！　ごはん、食べましょう！！\nカレーとラーメン、温かい！　ここ、寒い！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Food! Food‚ let’s eat!!\nCurry and ramen‚ warm! It’s cold here!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.2578212978,
      "endTime": 98.03482821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 98.2481613716
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "結局どうしたいのよ、こころは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you want to do‚ Kokoro!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2481613716,
      "endTime": 100.87142811620001,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4023.266839999991
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 102.0047630709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "はふぅ……生き返りました～\n温かくて美味しいお料理～！　北海道、最高ですねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahh… I’m alive~.\nWarm and delicious food~! Hokkaido is the best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.0714282116,
      "endTime": 113.3558499417,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 107.3333344778
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 113.54251678
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……現金なんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly… We’re still a long way from the destination.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.54251678,
      "endTime": 116.2235370875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、北海道ってやっぱり遠いんだね\nアメリカほどじゃないけどさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hokkaido is really far away‚ isn’t it?\nNot as far as America‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4368703683,
      "endTime": 122.786870559,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.9935369968
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2402_01_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……北海道に住んでるファンにとって\n本州でのライブに参加するのって、やっぱり大変よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right… It must be hard for fans living in Hokkaido\nto attend concerts in Honshu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.9935369968,
      "endTime": 130.48149619100002,
